<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="service.css">
    <title>Food Donation Services</title>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <nav class="navbar">
        <a href="/" class="logo">
            <img src="food.jpg" height="60px" width="140px" alt="Logo">
        </a>
        <div class="menu">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/about">About</a>
            <a href="/service" class="active">Services</a>
            <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <section id="services">
        <h1>Our Services</h1>
        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="service-card">
                <!-- Food Collection Image -->
                <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTPr2IitCxYTsdFGdv8njswJYZ4x1fA0qnM4g&amp;s"
                    alt="Food Collection Image">
                <h2>Food Collection</h2>
                <p>We collect surplus food from restaurants, hotels, events, and individuals. Our team ensures proper
                    handling and transportation of all donations.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <!-- Distribution Network Image -->
                <img src="https://www.shutterstock.com/image-vector/food-production-processing-distribution-chain-260nw-2044722146.jpg"
                    alt="Distribution Network Image">
                <h2>Distribution Network</h2>
                <p>Through our extensive network of local partners, we distribute food to shelters, food banks, and
                    communities in need.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <!-- Food Safety Image -->
                <img src="https://www.buysafetyposters.com/uploads/ProductZoom/prod0-English-188.jpg"
                    alt="Food Safety Image">
                <h2>Food Safety</h2>
                <p>Our trained staff ensures all donated food meets safety standards and is properly stored and handled
                    throughout the process.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <!-- Emergency Response Image -->
                <img src="https://cdn.statefoodsafety.com/blog/2020/12/RUTH_manager_teach_emergency_preparedness_food_workers_900px-c.jpg"
                    alt="Emergency Response Image">
                <h2>Emergency Response</h2>
                <p>We provide rapid food assistance during emergencies and natural disasters to affected communities.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <!-- Community Programs Image -->
                <img src="https://research.com/resized/uploads/community_Service_1_32f7dd3e77.jpg?format=large"
                    alt="Community Programs Image">
                <h2>Community Programs</h2>
                <p>We organize food drives and awareness programs to engage the community in fighting hunger.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <!-- Corporate Partnerships Image -->
                <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQ2a9GVfOPeJJUAvCGPl9rQZWJxhyw8AygCVQ&amp;s"
                    alt="Corporate Partnerships Image">
                <h2>Corporate Partnerships</h2>
                <p>We work with businesses to establish regular food donation programs and reduce food waste.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
